<h6 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:1:78">Start Giving Monthly Today. Change a Life Tomorrow.</h6>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:2:96">
	The Bed &amp; Bread Club is a monthly giving program powered by compassionate people like you who want to support their neighbors facing hunger and homelessness.
</p>
